{"tid":58280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界需要必要既雙重標準","createTime":"2016-12-28T16:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T13:13:11.000Z","uid":17696,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd2000b13e047181d7fd82944f16860e95452a2","tid":58280,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"例如以巴衝突咁<br />\n明顯係西方國家出賣左巴勒斯坦人<br />\n猶太人明顯係理虧<br />\n但係巴勒斯坦人係咩嚟？<br />\n穆斯林囉 穆斯林係咩嚟大家都清楚<br />\n逼害一個咁既民族有何問題？<br />\n穆斯林出哂名恐怖主義上腦 <br />\n佢地係危害緊成個世界 <br />\n世界唔係垃圾桶 唔係愛嚟裝垃圾的<br />\n繼續畀人權呢啲人呢個世界唔洗要<br />\n<br />\n停止譴責猶太人 <br />\n放棄眾生平等呢啲幻想<br />\n因為必要既雙重標準先可以保障到大多數"},{"pid":"7d1b4c5e70cdb843d501efeb0f7d8ce3201c6a55","tid":58280,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52404a6d00c34644498dff6e6d0372ebaf5ab9dd","tid":58280,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"方向正確，論述一般 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6acb0f47138449f2e7d09a586735003e947696e","tid":58280,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"根本單一面向嘅標準又點量度多維度嘅世界"},{"pid":"efed4d64b1155a2dccc364fe68b30d2e6c8bd5b0","tid":58280,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"It's the exception that makes the rule."},{"pid":"44c489a659ca3cfa42c642021e354d525a3b7b65","tid":58280,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:17:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3077dbae70911f853e4174fdd7be9046dbef2db7","tid":58280,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f342db24a9796bb28091b6316eb403e20ee1443","tid":58280,"uid":62103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"穆斯林喺指伊斯蘭教信徒，喺唔喺所有信伊斯蘭教嘅人